snippet.title: FOX n FORESTS - Gameplay 2018 - Gorgeous Gorge
snippet.description: Level 1:2 - Quickest route with 80% of all secrets left out for YOU to discover! Every level in FOX n FORESTS plays and feels differently, with Gorgeous Gorge being our melancholic, maze-like mountain stage.
